  "title": "Part time Retail sales Manager (Lighting and Design)",
  "description": "<p>We’re looking for passionate and aggressive <strong>Retail Sales Manager </strong>to share about lights and design for residential home owners.  Illuminating Asia offers an active online marketing and a well-defined training program with ready cliente to help all retail sales managers to succeed in building a career in sales with professional\ndevelopment.  Check out www.lunebrillante.sg on the patented products we carry. <br /></p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Need to handle indoor and outdoor sales requirements (working with interior designers)</li><li>Help out with marketing related functions and event</li><li>Work will include but not limited to admin, people management, inventory management, stock check, client servicing, service recovery and housekeeping.</li></ul><p><strong></strong><br /><strong>Preferred Skills and Attributes:</strong></p><ul><li>Able to commit to working 1 weekend and 2 weekdays.  Be prepared to support client and service management questions that comes in at odd hours.</li><li>Loves to do sales and focus in creating effective sales strategy and action plan.</li><li>Driven to meet sales target, work closely with existing sales team / colleagues / management</li><li>Good communication skills</li><li>Detail oriented </li><li>Preferably loves designs and meeting people<br /></li></ul><p></p><p></p><p></p><p><br /></p><p></p>",
