    "description": "<p><strong>Illuminating Asia Singapore Private Limited</strong>&nbsp;was founded in 2010. Since inception of the company, our vision has been set to offer our customers with high quality, energy efficient and affordable LED lighting solutions. We firmly believe in honesty, responsibility and commitment to all our clients and the development of the industry.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We always listen to our customers' needs and understand it before customizing our solutions for them. We believe going for the extra mile for our clients and ensuring our solution fit nicely to the requirements.&nbsp;<br>\n<br>\nBeing a specialist in LEDs lighting and displays, we have the know-how and is able to provide our customer quality products at competitive prices, LED consultation, installation, OEM / ODM services if required.&nbsp;We also have the capability to meet all urgent requests and constantly achieved half the industry average lead/production time,&nbsp;which is made possible because of our extensive and dynamic&nbsp;relationships with at least&nbsp;150 manufacturers for any of our product.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Therefore in Illuminating Asia, we strive to provide end-to-end LED lighting solutions, giving our customers a hassle free LED lighting experience.</p>",
